## Attribution

This project is a fork of [alfredang/notebooklm-mcp](https://github.com/alfredang/notebooklm-mcp)
(MIT License) and is built on top of [teng-lin/notebooklm-py](https://github.com/teng-lin/notebooklm-py)
(MIT License, Copyright (c) 2026 Teng Lin).

Substantial modifications: rewrite of MCP server to lazy initialization with
auto-refresh authentication, cookies-from-Chrome bypass (eliminating Playwright
login), 12 additional MCP tools (file/Drive sources + 9 artifact downloads +
wait utility), and bug fixes against current `notebooklm-py>=0.3.4` API.
